Program: Great Lives
Title: Sylvia Pankhurst
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0076433
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 Jun 2014
Barbara Castle and biographer Mary Davis discuss the life of suffragette Sylvia Pankhurst. With Joan Bakewell. From September 2001. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who has inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? Show less